---
import { Image } from "astro:assets";

import ScreenshotImg from "../assets/img/ss-ds.png";
---

<div class="py-16 pb-10 bg-gray-900 sm:py-32">
  <div class="px-6 mx-auto max-w-7xl lg:px-8">
    <div class="max-w-2xl mx-auto sm:text-center">
      <p class="text-3xl font-semibold leading-8 tracking-tighter text-cyan-300 sm:text-5xl">Kelola Database WhatsApp Dengan Mudah</p>
      <p class="mt-6 text-xl font-light text-gray-300 sm:text-2xl">Ubah cold market menjadi hot market ðŸ”¥</p>
    </div>
  </div>
  <div class="relative pt-16 overflow-hidden">
    <div class="px-6 mx-auto max-w-7xl lg:px-8">
      <Image
        src={ScreenshotImg}
        alt="A bird sitting on a nest of eggs."
        class="mb-[-12%] rounded-xl shadow-2xl ring-1 ring-white/10"
        width="2432"
        height="1442"
      />
      <div class="relative" aria-hidden="true">
        <div class="absolute -inset-x-20 bottom-0 bg-gradient-to-t from-gray-900 pt-[7%]"></div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
  <div class="px-6 mx-auto mt-16 max-w-7xl sm:mt-20 md:mt-24 lg:px-8">
    <dl
      class="grid max-w-2xl grid-cols-1 mx-auto text-base leading-7 text-gray-300 gap-x-6 gap-y-10 sm:text-lg sm:grid-cols-2 lg:mx-0 lg:max-w-none lg:grid-cols-3 lg:gap-x-8 lg:gap-y-16"
    >
      <div class="relative pl-16">
        <dt class="inline font-semibold text-white">
          <svg class="absolute w-12 h-12 left-1 top-1 text-cyan-500" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="transparent" stroke="currentColor" aria-hidden="true">
            <path
              fill-rule="evenodd"
              d="M15.75 9V5.25A2.25 2.25 0 0 0 13.5 3h-6a2.25 2.25 0 0 0-2.25 2.25v13.5A2.25 2.25 0 0 0 7.5 21h6a2.25 2.25 0 0 0 2.25-2.25V15m3 0 3-3m0 0-3-3m3 3H9"
              clip-rule="evenodd"></path>
          </svg>
          Connecting ->
        </dt>
        <dd class="inline font-light">Sambungkan WhatsApp ke Dripsender, gunakan fitur training new number</dd>
      </div>
      <div class="relative pl-16">
        <dt class="inline font-semibold text-white">
          <svg class="absolute w-12 h-12 left-1 top-1 text-cyan-500" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="transparent" stroke="currentColor" aria-hidden="true">
            <path
              fill-rule="evenodd"
              d="M7.5 7.5h-.75A2.25 2.25 0 0 0 4.5 9.75v7.5a2.25 2.25 0 0 0 2.25 2.25h7.5a2.25 2.25 0 0 0 2.25-2.25v-7.5a2.25 2.25 0 0 0-2.25-2.25h-.75m0-3-3-3m0 0-3 3m3-3v11.25m6-2.25h.75a2.25 2.25 0 0 1 2.25 2.25v7.5a2.25 2.25 0 0 1-2.25 2.25h-7.5a2.25 2.25 0 0 1-2.25-2.25v-.75"
              clip-rule="evenodd"></path>
          </svg>
          Upload Database ->
        </dt>
        <dd class="inline font-light">Unggah database WhatsApp calon pelanggan yang Anda punya ke Dripsender</dd>
      </div>
      <div class="relative pl-16">
        <dt class="inline font-semibold text-white">
          <svg class="absolute w-12 h-12 left-1 top-1 text-cyan-500" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="transparent" stroke="currentColor" aria-hidden="true">
            <path
              fill-rule="evenodd"
              d="M19.5 12c0-1.232-.046-2.453-.138-3.662a4.006 4.006 0 0 0-3.7-3.7 48.678 48.678 0 0 0-7.324 0 4.006 4.006 0 0 0-3.7 3.7c-.017.22-.032.441-.046.662M19.5 12l3-3m-3 3-3-3m-12 3c0 1.232.046 2.453.138 3.662a4.006 4.006 0 0 0 3.7 3.7 48.656 48.656 0 0 0 7.324 0 4.006 4.006 0 0 0 3.7-3.7c.017-.22.032-.441.046-.662M4.5 12l3 3m-3-3-3 3"
              clip-rule="evenodd"></path>
          </svg>
          Campaign Marketing ->
        </dt>
        <dd class="inline font-light">Buat campaign marketing terjadwal dan otomatis untuk pelanggan baru / lama</dd>
      </div>
      <div class="relative pl-16">
        <dt class="inline font-semibold text-white">
          <svg class="absolute w-12 h-12 left-1 top-1 text-cyan-500" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="transparent" stroke="currentColor" aria-hidden="true">
            <path
              fill-rule="evenodd"
              d="M12 3c2.755 0 5.455.232 8.083.678.533.09.917.556.917 1.096v1.044a2.25 2.25 0 0 1-.659 1.591l-5.432 5.432a2.25 2.25 0 0 0-.659 1.591v2.927a2.25 2.25 0 0 1-1.244 2.013L9.75 21v-6.568a2.25 2.25 0 0 0-.659-1.591L3.659 7.409A2.25 2.25 0 0 1 3 5.818V4.774c0-.54.384-1.006.917-1.096A48.32 48.32 0 0 1 12 3Z"
              clip-rule="evenodd"></path>
          </svg>

          Target Funneling ->
        </dt>
        <dd class="inline font-light">Rancang sistem funnel untuk memperoleh target pelanggan yang hot market</dd>
      </div>
      <div class="relative pl-16">
        <dt class="inline font-semibold text-white">
          <svg class="absolute w-12 h-12 left-1 top-1 text-cyan-500" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="transparent" stroke="currentColor" aria-hidden="true">
            <path
              fill-rule="evenodd"
              d="M7.5 8.25h9m-9 3H12m-9.75 1.51c0 1.6 1.123 2.994 2.707 3.227 1.129.166 2.27.293 3.423.379.35.026.67.21.865.501L12 21l2.755-4.133a1.14 1.14 0 0 1 .865-.501 48.172 48.172 0 0 0 3.423-.379c1.584-.233 2.707-1.626 2.707-3.228V6.741c0-1.602-1.123-2.995-2.707-3.228A48.394 48.394 0 0 0 12 3c-2.392 0-4.744.175-7.043.513C3.373 3.746 2.25 5.14 2.25 6.741v6.018Z"
              clip-rule="evenodd"></path>
          </svg>
          Automation Bot ->
        </dt>
        <dd class="inline font-light">Buat bot tak terbatas untuk menjawab chat dari pelanggan secara otomatis</dd>
      </div>
      <div class="relative pl-16">
        <dt class="inline font-semibold text-white">
          <svg class="absolute w-12 h-12 left-1 top-1 text-cyan-500" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="transparent" stroke="currentColor" aria-hidden="true">
            <path fill-rule="evenodd" d="m3.75 13.5 10.5-11.25L12 10.5h8.25L9.75 21.75 12 13.5H3.75Z" clip-rule="evenodd"></path>
          </svg>
          Artificial Intelligence ->
        </dt>
        <dd class="inline font-light">Buat materi campaign dengan cepat dan mudah menggunakan AI</dd>
      </div>
    </dl>
  </div>
</div>
